title: FUBAR DeskFiller 2014
description:
FUBAR DeskFiller 2014
---------------------

A new version of this annoying, and potential harmful application.

As always:
Upon installation, you will get 2 warnings about what you are about to install.
Installation takes a few seconds.
And after installation, nothing more will happen.

Next time, and every time, any user logs into Windows, this application will start and fill up the desktop with thousands and thousands of completely random and useless files.
And it will do so very quick.
And it will just keep on going...


Here is how to uninstall:
- Boot up in Safe-Mode.
- Open the Registry Editor (regedit.exe).
- Browse to this key:
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion/Run.
- Delete the value named "FUBAR DeskFiller 2014".


/Ubehage
